algtestjclient

Class SingleModeTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • algtestjclient.SingleModeTest

  • public class SingleModeTest
extends java.lang.Object
    AlgTest class to test smart card supported algorithms using multiple APDU's each testing one algorithm. Requires 'AlgTestSinglePerApdu' applet installed on card. Supports running without connected card using jCardSim. (www.jcardsim.org)
